2c2d96a48a7a7dce2e369d9da826da9a2ed34371","tid":1941751,"uid":141286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T16:40:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和你登記做選民</span></span><br />\n凡登記DSE考生必考靚Grade<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n選民登記填表機<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk2020.vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ7c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=15704ec3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk2020.vote</a><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">只要在2020年7月25日或以前年滿18歲，今年5月2日前可登記做選民\n\n18歲生日快樂 即刻登記做選民</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/75XjnXd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F75XjnXd.jpg&h=5bfa9f32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/M8STBFS.jpg\" /><br />\n另外亦可選擇填寫表格<br />\n選民登記表格[/b][/size=5]可循以下途徑索取表格：<br />\n1。各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ7c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=76930b31\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n2。公共屋邨辦事處（大家樓下就有）<br />\n3。選舉事務處地址：[/gold]<br />\n-&gt;香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓<br />\n-&gt;九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓<br />\n4。地方選區選民新登記申請表：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C%29.pdf&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ7c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=a505c119\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n選民資料網上查閱系統<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ7c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=1a42b36b\" target=